metadata.creator: AlYankovic
metadata.title: "Weird Al" Yankovic - I Lost On Jeopardy

tracks.text: Cameramen get ready on a TV set
Al adjusts his glasses.
They open their jackets, revealing diplomas.
Al sings worriedly at us.
Art Flemming walks out onto the Jeopardy set, and gestures to a blue curtain, which moves aside.
The cameramen turn to us and sing.
Categories include Nuclear Physics, World Geography, Food, Potpourri, Famous Accordion Players.
World Geography for $20, Number of Bricks in the Great Wall of China.
The plumber clasps his hands and shakes them as his score goes up.
Al looks worried.
Food, $20, Secret ingredient found in both cheese whiz and crazy glue
Daily Double, This German Baroness could suck the chrome off a fender.
complex math equations
His head spins. Art rolls his eyes.
Al has 0 points.
Producers watch and smoke.
Producers turn to us and sing.
The architect, with $380, points at TV Themes for $80. The quesiton is chinese characters.
The architect looks pleased. Al looks confused.
Art sticks out his tongue at Al.
2 people approach Al and pick him up. He grabs the podium, and rips off a panel.
They carry him as he struggles, brandishing the panel.
Art frowns and gives 2 thumbs down.
Al is carried away, past the Price is Right sign.
Cameramen and producers sing.
Models coo
Art sways and waves
Everyone in the studio sways and waves. Doors marked Stage 5 open.
The men swing and toss Al out the doors.
Al flies into the back of an open convertible. The driver turns behind and looks at us. It's Greg Kihn.
In the passenger seat, a bride opens a champagne bottle, and pours champagne out the side.
Al looks around as the car drives off.
Cut to black
